    <div class="font15"><h1 class="">Dream11 Overview</h1></div>
    <div class="font15">
      <p>Dream11 are the biggest Fantasy Cricket operator in the world and have grown massively since initially being founded in 2012. &nbsp;Dream11 have over 4 million registered users spread across India and USA and host the biggest Fantasy Cricket contests currently available online. &nbsp;Their large player base means the site are able to offer the biggest guaranteed prizepools to Indian Fantasy Cricket players which gives the opportunity to win bigger prizes at Dream11 than any competitor site.</p>
      <p><strong>Website:</strong> www.dream11.com.</p>
      <p><strong>Welcome Bonus Offer:&nbsp;</strong>Dream11 do not currently offer a specific Welcome Bonus but do offer cash bonuses during special promotional events. &nbsp;Registered players will be notified via email and other communication channels of these special promotional periods.</p>
      <p>Deposit Methods Offered:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><span style="font-weight: 400;">PayUMoney.</span></li>
        <li><span style="font-weight: 400;">PayTM.</span></li>
        <li>Directpay.com</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong> Is it Legal:&nbsp;</strong>Dream11 have dedicated a whole section on their website to explain why as a skill game, Dream11 fantasy contests are legal for players to participate in. You can read further<a href="https://fantasycricket.dream11.com/in/legality."> details by clicking here.</a> &nbsp;Please note however that as the laws in the states of Assam and Odisha are not clear as to whether skill games can be played for a fee, at the current time <span style="font-weight: 400;">residents of Assam and Odisha are not permitted to participate in the paid formats of the Dream11 Fantasy Cricket, Kabaddi or Football Games. Residents of Assam and Odisha may, however, participate in the ‘free-to-play’ version of the Dream11 Game.</span></p>
      <p><strong>Refer a Friend Offer:&nbsp;</strong>Refer a friend to Dream11 and both you and your friend will receive a R.s. 250 cash bonus once the successful mobile, PAN and email verification of your friend has taken place. <a href="https://fantasycricket.dream11.com/in/leagues">&nbsp;Click here for more details.</a></p>
