      <p><strong>Dream11 Mobile: &nbsp;</strong>Dream11 have both an iOS app that is available from the Apple App store, and also an Android App that can be downloaded. &nbsp;<a href="https://fantasycricket.dream11.com/in/frequently-asked-questions">Click here for further details</a> of the mobile offering.</p>
      <p><strong>Dream11 customer support: &nbsp;C</strong>ustomer support is via email and phone however the phone support is only available to players&nbsp;who have participated in a league with an entry fee of Rs.300.</p>
      <h3>Signing Up a Dream11 Account.</h3>
      <p>To sign up an account with Dream11,&nbsp;users must be over the age of 18 years old and reside in India. The sign up process itself is very simple&nbsp;and users can register by clicking on the ‘Sign Up’ button in the top right hand corner of the website or on mobile or tablet by downloading the available app for Android or iOS devices.</p>
      <p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6197" src="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Homepage.jpg" alt="Dream11" width="700" height="429" srcset="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Homepage.jpg 1063w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Homepage-300x184.jpg 300w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Homepage-768x471.jpg 768w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Homepage-1024x628.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></p>
      <h3>Dream11 Help.</h3>
      <p>The <a href="https://fantasycricket.dream11.com/in/howtoplay">Help Section </a>of the website can be accessed via a link in the top menu bar as indicated in the image below. &nbsp;The Help section is extremely comprehensive in giving full information on how to play the game and answering Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs).</p>
      <p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6202" src="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Help.jpg" alt="Dream11" width="700" height="568" srcset="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Help.jpg 819w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Help-300x244.jpg 300w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Help-768x624.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></p>
      <h3>Depositing to your&nbsp;Account.</h3>
      <p>After you have registered your account and logged in, you will have the option to deposit funds so that you can enter real money contests. &nbsp;To deposit funds, just click on the red plus sign next to the red wallet icon in the top right hand corner of the homepage and you will access the screen below. &nbsp;At this point you need to follow the instructions which will allow you to deposit funds safely and securely.</p>
      <p><b><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6198" src="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Deposit-funds.jpg" alt="Dream11" width="700" height="454" srcset="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Deposit-funds.jpg 926w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Deposit-funds-300x195.jpg 300w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Deposit-funds-768x498.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></b><br>
      To check your total account balance including any bonus cash funds then simply click on the red wallet in the top right hand corner of the page.</p>
      <h3>The Dream11 Game Lobby.</h3>
      <p>When logging in you will automatically access the main game lobby which is where you can decide which Fantasy Cricket games you wish to participate in. &nbsp; The lobby will contain games that you can enter for fun or for real money. &nbsp;The red circle below indicates the icons to click to access your account wallet or to add money as described.</p>
      <p>The lobby can look very intimidating for new players so here at India Fantasy Cricket&nbsp;we want to guide you through the key sections. We will do this by going through the steps required to enter a Dream11&nbsp;game. There is a lot going on in the lobby so it is great to take some time and explore all that the site&nbsp;has to offer.</p>
      <p>In the image below, the Cricket tab is currently clicked on however to display Football, Kabaddi or Multi-Match games then users just need to click on the relevant tab.</p>
      <p>Below the sport choice are the specific Cricket matches that Fantasy games are being based on so you can select the game you are interested in most.</p>
      <p>Below the cricket matches are some of the key highlights of Dream11 including their ‘Grand League’ which is their biggest real money league. Users also have the option to ‘Challenge Friends’ by creating their own league or to get R.s 250 credited to their account by the ‘Refer a friend section’.</p>
      <p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6200" src="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-1.jpg" alt="Dream11" width="700" height="542" srcset="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-1.jpg 852w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-1-300x232.jpg 300w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-1-768x595.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></p>
      <p>Users will then see a selection of real money games, and the image of a Cricket pitch which currently has no team line-up created. &nbsp;Scrolling further down the page, users can see the wide range of Fantasy Cricket games that Dream11 offer on the specific highlighted match. &nbsp; At the bottom of the page are ‘Skill’ games which require no real money to play but do not have cash prizes. Fantasy Cricket skill games are a great way to practice the game and improve your skill level without the risk of losing money.</p>
      <p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6201" src="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-3.jpg" alt="Dream11" width="700" height="523" srcset="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-3.jpg 819w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-3-300x224.jpg 300w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-game-lobby-3-768x574.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></p>
      <h3>Entering a Dream11 Contest</h3>
      <p>Clicking on the blue join button from the main lobby will take users through to the team selection zone. &nbsp;Here users are required to pick the players they want to represent their team within the set budget of 100 ‘credits’. &nbsp;Players are selected by clicking on the green plus button from the left hand side player list. &nbsp;A selected player will then appear on the team graphic on the right hand side. &nbsp;A player can be removed and changed by clicking on the red cross above their name on the graphic image.</p>
      <p>Dream11 also requires users to pick a Captain and Vice-Captain for their team and this is done by clicking on the button circled below.</p>
      <h3><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6204" src="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection.jpg" alt="Dream11" width="700" height="492" srcset="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection.jpg 941w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection-300x211.jpg 300w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection-768x539.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></h3>
      <p>Captain and Vice-Captain selection box.</p>
      <p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6205" src="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection-Captain-and-VC.jpg" alt="Dream11" width="700" height="478" srcset="http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection-Captain-and-VC.jpg 977w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection-Captain-and-VC-300x205.jpg 300w, http://www.indiafantasycricket.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dream11-Team-Selection-Captain-and-VC-768x524.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></p>
      <p>Once users are happy with their team and do not want to make any further changes then they just need to click on the ‘Save team’ button at the bottom of the page.</p>
      <h3>Inviting friends to play in a Dream11&nbsp;game.</h3>
      <p>One of the great features of Dream11 is the ability to easily invite friends to play in the same games as you. &nbsp;After you have entered a game, the join button will turn to a green ‘invite’ button as displayed below.</p>
